{"tid":1258490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無一個政府同保皇狗賣港database?比每個人知道政府點切佢忽肉？","createTime":"2019-06-26T06:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T08:04:34.000Z","uid":172349,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"82834b0562ede08576586132296d86f11e64c225","tid":1258490,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"1:萬億元人工島以及其他相關高鐵工程<br />\n2: 政府減醫療撥款<br />\n3: 每日150個香港無權拒絕既新移民<br />\n4: 國歌法<br />\n5: 推行中文教學矮化英語<br />\n6<br />\n7<br />\n8<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n其實每個香港人，總有幾條惡事令佢受害<br />\n<br />\n點樣有條理咁比七百萬人知道<br />\n等每一個香港人都清楚依家政府具體上有邊幾條惡事令佢地受害<br />\n<br />\n當每個香港人都具體明白有咩惡事切到佢地忽肉，個力量或者會好大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n具體上點整？例如整一張長輩圖，每個香港人睇完都有幾個point 桔到佢？"},{"pid":"9c43f473f5512c90529e8277e0b6bd82c420836e","tid":1258490,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.legcovotes.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legcovotes.net%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=8fbc7ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.legcovotes.net/</a>"},{"pid":"20b19f1389d7e29c760cabc1d56b4925b7219cbe","tid":1258490,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c43f473f5512c90529e8277e0b6bd82c420836e","tid":1258490,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.legcovotes.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legcovotes.net%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=8fbc7ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.legcovotes.net/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"好似死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bfbb91a302bc194109bc94f58fda95558e414a","tid":1258490,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:46:45.000Z","msg":"要一個方法令人用三兩分鐘睇完，桔到佢幾下"},